  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>This coiling band is made of jade carved into the shape of a sea drake. If the wearer can cast summon nature's ally spells, the wearer adds forest drakeB2 and shadow drakeB4 to the 4th-level list of monsters he can summon with those spells, adds flame drakeB2 to the 5th-level list, adds frost drakeB2 to the 6th-level list, and adds desert drakeB3 to the 9th-level list. Also, once per day on command the wearer can use this ring to summon a shadow drake, as if by the summon nature's ally IV spell.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> </p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Forge Ring, greater magic fang, summon nature's ally IV</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Advanced Class Guide",
